<Document>
  <name>Montgomery County — Unmapped Historical Markers</name>
  <description>THC markers in Montgomery County without an HMDB id (isMissing excluded). 17 with THC coords; 0 geocoded from address; 9 omitted (no usable address).</description>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Baker Cemetery</name>
